<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-054449187.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-054449187.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=cfc03875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-054449187.html</a>"},{"pid":"0a91aa9ce1c21fef7ef3ee226f8b9ef3efe09f00","tid":1303788,"uid":277916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>書展行山攻略</ins></strong></span><br />\n香港成日俾人話係文化沙漠，覺得行個書展就可以增進文化氣息，見一眾巴絲都對書展咁有興趣，小弟都想拋磚講下呢座山可以點樣行，幫呢個文化沙漠增添啲人氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR嘅話可以淨係睇紅字<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">入場門券：</span></ins></strong><br />\n眾所鳩知，外地旅客係有10蚊優惠，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公眾人士只要喺上晝12點前買飛</span></strong></span>，都可以享受10蚊票價優惠，所謂行山要趁早，大家都係盡早出門口<br />\n<br />\n而講到優惠啦喎，又點少得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超級書迷證，80蚊就可以全天候隨時入場，堪稱書展放題證</span></strong>，對於鍾意多刷嘅朋友係最方便不過<br />\n但要注意呢張書迷證係要提交個人資料同一張彩色嘅相，不過咁，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">書迷證入咗場之後係唔需要帶喺身度</span></span></strong>，所以佢係分唔到你究竟係普通飛定係放題證入場，請一眾行山人士自行評估風險再作考慮，申請表可以喺呢度download：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/SuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fhkbfweb%2FContent%2Fuploads%2Fdocs%2FSuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=5d8b6ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/SuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf</a><br />\n呢張證去到7月16號之前都仲可以申請，申請地點包括天主教香港教區辦公室，其他地方如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/2019SuperPassList-Cn.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fhkbfweb%2FContent%2Fuploads%2Fdocs%2F2019SuperPassList-Cn.pdf&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=b9434d05\" target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/2019SuperPassList-Cn.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n如果各位行山人士唔鍾意面對面買飛或者唔想浪費行山時間喺排隊度<br />\n不妨考慮下喺7-11或者OK便利店買飛，足跡遍佈全港，總有一間喺左近<br />\n<br />\n詳情可參閱書展官方網站嘅票務詳情：<a href=\"http://hkbookfair.hktdc.com/tc/Visitor/Ticketing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkbookfair.hktdc.com%2Ftc%2FVisitor%2FTicketing.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=e8a7076b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkbookfair.hktdc.com/tc/Visitor/Ticketing.html</a><br />\n<br />\n想又有錢收又有山行，就可以留意各大招聘網站嘅書展part time，宜家仲請緊人架！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">行山指引：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n書展保安係有清晰指示，除非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你舉牌同叫口號</span></span></strong>，<br />\n否則佢哋係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>無權</strong></span></span>趕你走架<br />\n例如：背囊掛住咗張標語，或者痴住喺件衫度等等<br />\n所以請各位巴絲發揮創意，喺沉默之中爆發你哋聲音<br />\n<br />\n詳情可參閱書展官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hktdc.com/mis/vrr/tc/%E8%A8%AA%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktdc.com%2Fmis%2Fvrr%2Ftc%2F%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%2589%2587%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%258F.html&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=50c75450\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hktdc.com/mis/vrr/tc/%E8%A8%AA%E5%AE%A2%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%8F.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">行山景點：</span></ins></strong><br />\n書展咁大，由新翼到舊翼，由一樓到五樓，都有參展商同N咁多活動搞<br />\n不妨集中火力，專攻一樓嘅HALL1<br />\n<br />\nHALL 1幾乎集合哂所有巴絲要支持嘅愛國書店<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三聯書店：1E-B04,1E-B16,1E-A24<br />\n中華書局：1D-C02,1E-A14<br />\n商務印書館： 1E-A04,1D-D02<br />\n香港教育圖書公司：1D-D02<br />\n天地圖書： 1D-A02,1D-A16<br />\n中和出版： 1D-D28<br />\n萬里圖書：1D-B02<br />\n聯合書刊物流：1D-C18,1D-D16<br />\n澳門文化廣場：1E-A20</span><br />\n<br />\n除咗書商之外，大家仲可以留意喺場內嘅政府部門同青年組織<br />\n每年都會有高官去香港青年協會嘅攤位，唔知今年有咩人呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">攤位號碼： 1A-B01</span><br />\n<br />\n如果得閒嘅先去HALL 3：<br />\n新雅文化： 3E-C04,3E-C12,3E-C22,3E-D04,3E-D12,3E-D22<br />\n但其實唔太建議去HALL 3，因為HALL 3係兒童天地，會有好多家長同小朋友，所以都係集中專攻番HALL 1好啲<br />\n<br />\n地圖如下：<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkbookfair.hktdc.com/Content/images/booth/1E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkbookfair.hktdc.com%2FContent%2Fimages%2Fbooth%2F1E.png&h=c63778fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">場內活動：</span></ins></strong><br />\n書展暑假活動多，歡迎各位場內人士踴躍參與，亦誠邀各位集思廣益，睇下有咩適合嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日星期六<br />\n下午3:00 至 下午4:30<br />\n《香港超越內耗》論壇暨新書發布會<br />\n分類： 本地文化歷史講座系列<br />\n地點： 會議室 S226-227<br />\n講者： <strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屈穎妍</span></span></ins></strong>、<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>雷鼎鳴</ins></span></span></strong>、阮紀宏、邱立本、楊志剛、劉瀾昌、潘麗瓊、譚衛兒、何漢權、周八駿、陳莊勤、邵盧善、陳建強、李春、江迅<br />\n主持： 何亮亮<br />\n備註： 網上登記已截止，主辦單位將根據現場清況，按次序安排登記及未登記之人士進場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39d7ae40d0531ca4ecf754d9668877aa6bd4bf2","tid":1303788,"uid":276317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a91aa9ce1c21fef7ef3ee226f8b9ef3efe09f00","tid":1303788,"uid":277916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>書展行山攻略</ins></strong></span><br />\n香港成日俾人話係文化沙漠，覺得行個書展就可以增進文化氣息，見一眾巴絲都對書展咁有興趣，小弟都想拋磚講下呢座山可以點樣行，幫呢個文化沙漠增添啲人氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR嘅話可以淨係睇紅字<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">入場門券：</span></ins></strong><br />\n眾所鳩知，外地旅客係有10蚊優惠，而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公眾人士只要喺上晝12點前買飛</span></strong></span>，都可以享受10蚊票價優惠，所謂行山要趁早，大家都係盡早出門口<br />\n<br />\n而講到優惠啦喎，又點少得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超級書迷證，80蚊就可以全天候隨時入場，堪稱書展放題證</span></strong>，對於鍾意多刷嘅朋友係最方便不過<br />\n但要注意呢張書迷證係要提交個人資料同一張彩色嘅相，不過咁，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">書迷證入咗場之後係唔需要帶喺身度</span></span></strong>，所以佢係分唔到你究竟係普通飛定係放題證入場，請一眾行山人士自行評估風險再作考慮，申請表可以喺呢度download：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/SuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fhkbfweb%2FContent%2Fuploads%2Fdocs%2FSuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=5d8b6ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/SuperPassforBookLovers-ApplicationForm-2019.pdf</a><br />\n呢張證去到7月16號之前都仲可以申請，申請地點包括天主教香港教區辦公室，其他地方如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/hkbfweb/Content/uploads/docs/2019SuperPassList-Cn.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fhkbfweb%2FContent%2Fuploads%2Fdocs%2F2019SuperPassList-Cn.pdf&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSCyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2B